column16: Anthony Gose lines out to left fielder Ben Francisco.

Rajai Davis strikes out on a foul tip.
James Loney grounds out to first baseman Carlos Pena.
With Cody Ross batting, Jacoby Ellsbury caught stealing 3rd base, catcher Stephen Vogt to third baseman Sean Rodriguez.

Jacoby Ellsbury singles on a ground ball to third baseman Sean Rodriguez.
Adam Jones flies out to center fielder B.   Upton.
J.   Hardy homers (21) on a fly ball to left field.   Nate McLouth scores.
